  <summary date="2021-10-29T14:32:30Z" status="Introduced in House">Green Climate Fund Authorization Act of 2021

This bill authorizes $4 billion in both FY2022 and FY2023 for U.S. contributions to the Green Climate Fund (a fund established under the United Nations Framework Convention on Climate Change to finance projects that address climate change).</summary>
